import React from "react";
import "./styles.scss";
import { Box, Grid, Typography, Divider } from "@material-ui/core";

export default function Home() {
  return (
    <Box className="home-admin bgr-admin pt-5">
      <Grid container className="list-top px-3" spacing={1}>
        <Grid item xs>
          <Box className="list-top-item">
            <Typography className="text-box" variant="body1" color="#999">
              Used Space
            </Typography>
            <Typography
              className="text-box"
              component="p"
              xs={{ fontSize: "1.4em" }}
              color="#333"
            >
              49/50GB
            </Typography>
          </Box>
          <Divider sx={{ textAlign: "center", padding: "10px" }} />
          <Box></Box>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs>
          <Box></Box>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs>
          <Box></Box>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs>
          <Box></Box>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
    </Box>
  );
}
